data.description: GREAT RANCH STYLE HOME, GEM in the subdivision of Courthouse Woods!!!  You will see the carefully maintained front yard, paved driveway and covered front porch welcome you. Once you enter the house there are large sized 3 bedroom, 2 full bath with a spacious living room that is open to the kitchen with cathedral ceilings and new kitchen cabinet, new dishwasher.  Large deck in the back yard is perfect to relax or entertain your guests! Not to mention the fully fenced rear yard,  new roof 2018, new HVAC 2016.  There are well maintained 3 shed for all the storages you need.  MUST SEE!!! Please make an appointment on the Showing Time!!!
